data.description: Nestled on a sprawling 1.37-acre lot, this stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom brick home is a testament to both elegance and functionality. The formal dining room offers a sophisticated space for entertaining guests, making every meal a special occasion. The gorgeous office/sitting room has a beautiful double door for privacy, if needed. The heart of the home lies in the well-appointed kitchen, seamlessly connected to the living room, creating an open and inviting layout. The kitchen is adorned with oak cabinets, granite countertops, and a convenient island – a perfect gathering spot for family and friends. Adjacent to the kitchen, a spacious living room is centered around a stone electric fireplace that can also be wood-burning, not only adding a touch of rustic charm but also capable of efficiently heating the entire home. The thoughtful design of this home extends to the library with awe inspiring book shelves, as well as an elongated desk top capable of three work spaces. The library only gets better when you find the ladder leading to the loft. The master bedroom is a sanctuary of comfort, offering generous space, his and hers closets, and a master bathroom that epitomizes luxury. Dual sinks, a Jacuzzi tub, and a standalone shower complete the spa-like experience, and includes built in cabinets. The practicality of this home is evident in the spacious laundry room, making household chores a breeze. Two guest bedrooms share a well-appointed hall bathroom featuring double sinks, a stand-up shower, and a luxurious jacuzzi tub. Tile floors flow seamlessly through the hallway and kitchen, ensuring easy maintenance and durability. The thoughtful design extends to the two-car attached garage with a workshop, providing both convenience and functionality. Outside, the expansive yard offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities and gatherings. A beautiful large concrete circle drive and a foundation for a shop was installed on the next-door lot. Call today!
